{"tid":1614970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完尋晚大圍之後, 希望大家仲記得天琦對所有香港人講過既嘢","createTime":"2019-10-03T02:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T03:03:01.000Z","uid":175119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"938a903ad97825e2337732921387d2e196966210","tid":1614970,"uid":175119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:57:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PN41RYS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPN41RYS.jpg&h=73ac2e84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gsa07xm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGsa07xm.jpg&h=67d3df3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X1UEDD9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX1UEDD9.jpg&h=166970ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QJvDUci.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQJvDUci.jpg&h=30f96c3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u1SbuLu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu1SbuLu.gif&h=07645a2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好明白近呢4個月既抗爭都令到大家身心疲累<br />\n茶飯不思 睡不安寧<br />\n每次合埋雙眼 一次又一次呈現出發夢見到過既深刻情景<br />\n當整個運動去到樽頸位既時候<br />\n太多嘢要去整合處理同時<br />\n希望大家唔好俾呢個垃圾香港政府/狗共/黑警愚弄<br />\n佢哋每一刻都係想利用可恥既手段令到成個運動升温<br />\n就係想我哋用仇恨嚟遮蓋我哋本來既目標<br />\n尋日班狗冇主動出擊 <br />\n亦可以理解成將我哋一面倒既行為喺媒體上面放大<br />\n無錯 從來都係呢招<br />\n尋晚喺大圍既現場直播 <br />\n好彩手足壓得住度氣先冇令到成件事引致不可收拾地步<br />\n行動係要有 但係要清晰<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n不分化 不割席 兄弟爬山<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pyhF7xL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpyhF7xL.jpg&h=2d759785&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25257efcc0a5cd669063954b806db398a7ffec81","tid":1614970,"uid":175119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}